				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\text{Gain }=\frac{1}{2}\left[\frac{{G}_{L}^{2}}{{H}_{L}+\lambda }+\frac{{G}_{R}^{2}}{{H}_{R}+\lambda }-\frac{{\left({G}_{L}+{G}_{R}\right)}^{2}}{{H}_{L}+{H}_{R}+\lambda }\right]-\gamma$$\end{document}Gain=12GL2HL+λ+GR2HR+λ-GL+GR2HL+HR+λ-γ
